# Tiny Threat Intelligence Platform (TIP)

A simple, terminal-based Threat Intelligence Platform built in Python.  
This project downloads a public feed of malicious domains and lets you check any domain for malicious activity.

## Features

- Downloads malicious domains from [URLhaus](https://urlhaus.abuse.ch/)  
- Stores domains in an SQLite database (`iocs.db`)  
- Terminal interface to check multiple domains for malicious status  
- Shows a sample of collected indicators for easy demo
- Cool ASCII banner for professional presentation

## How to Run

```bash
cd ~/tiny-tip
source venv/bin/activate
python3 collect_and_show.py
